## Prompt

You are a **senior product designer, UX engineer, and frontend architect**.

Your task is to **analyze an existing CodePen sample and evolve it into a modern, production-grade Catering company website**.

Do not simply replicate the sample — **derive a design system and improve the UX, layout, and visual hierarchy significantly**.

Before generating code, think step by step and first produce the design system and layout architecture.

