# 11 Icon System (Prefer SVG Icons)

All icons used in the website must be SVG-based, not bitmap images or icon fonts.

Requirements
Prefer inline SVG icons or a reusable SVG icon component system
Icons must scale cleanly across devices
Icons should inherit color from CSS (currentColor) when possible
Ensure icons remain sharp on high-resolution displays
Avoid PNG/JPG icons
Icon Style

Icons should follow a consistent visual style:

minimalist
thin stroke
geometric
modern

